tvshowdetails.label: American Horror Story
tvshowdetails.plot: American Horror Story is a horror-drama television franchise created and produced by Ryan Murphy and Brad Falchuk. Described as an anthology series, each season is conceived as a self-contained miniseries, following a disparate set of characters and settings, and a storyline with its own "beginning, middle and end".
tvshowdetails.title: American Horror Story

1.label: 1x01. Pilot
1.plot: A therapist and his family move across the country to escape their troubled past but quickly discover that their new home comes with its own horrific baggage.
1.title: Pilot

1.label: 1x02. Home Invasion
1.plot: Vivien and Violet get themselves caught in a dangerous situation. Meanwhile, Ben goes back to Boston to fix a mistake that he made.
1.title: Home Invasion

1.label: 1x03. Murder House
1.plot: Vivien learns the horrific truth about the house's first residents and Ben's visitor causes him to further unravel about what really happened in the haunted house. Constance and Moira have their history revealed.
1.title: Murder House

1.label: 1x04. Halloween (1)
1.plot: The line between the living and the dead blurs on Halloween. Two of the house's previous residents give the Harmons decorating advice.
1.title: Halloween (1)

1.label: 1x05. Halloween (2)
1.plot: Tate comes face to face with his past, and Ben and Vivien are haunted by a new houseguest before Halloween night comes to an end.
1.title: Halloween (2)

1.label: 1x06. Piggy, Piggy
1.plot: Constance enlists Violet's assistance with Tate. Ben helps a new patient confront his fears.
1.title: Piggy, Piggy

1.label: 1x07. Open House
1.plot: Moira persuades a buyer to make an offer while Constance and Larry work against her efforts.
1.title: Open House

1.label: 1x08. Rubber Man
1.plot: The man in the rubber suit is revealed.
1.title: Rubber Man

1.label: 1x09. Spooky Little Girl
1.plot: One of history's most famous murder victims pays the house a visit. Constance discovers more of Tate's bad behavior.
1.title: Spooky Little Girl

1.label: 1x10. Smoldering Children
1.plot: Violet learns about the rules of the house. The truth about Larry's condition is explained. Constance is interrogated by the police.
1.title: Smoldering Children

1.label: 1x11. Birth
1.plot: Vivien gives birth. Tate and Violet attempt to rid the house of some of its ghosts for good.
1.title: Birth

1.label: 1x12. Afterbirth
1.plot: In the aftermath of family tragedy, Ben tries to take his child out of the Murder House. Meanwhile, Violet and Vivien accustom themselves to their new living arrangements, Constance raises Tate's child as her own and a new family buys the house.
1.title: Afterbirth

2.label: 2x01. Welcome to Briarcliff
2.plot: Terrifying evils blur the boundaries between reality and insanity at the Briarcliff Manor.

2.label: 2x04. I Am Anne Frank (1)

2.label: 2x05. I Am Anne Frank (2)

2.title: I Am Anne Frank (2)

2.label: 2x06. The Origins of Monstrosity

2.title: The Origins of Monstrosity

2.label: 2x07. Dark Cousin

3.label: 3x02. Boy Parts

4.label: 4x06. Bullseye
